{"tid":58969,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"覺不覺鋼鋸嶺超越左雷霆救兵","createTime":"2016-12-29T09:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T03:57:51.000Z","uid":45749,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9092e9718436fda843a6de6d77da1f92c2b4e1b","tid":58969,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"第一段文戲 講toss既愛情唔悶有笑位 <br />\n第二段過渡 講toss入伍既辛路歷程 等觀眾慢慢代入主角的角度<br />\n末段戰爭場面同初段愛情小品形成極大反差 完全冇畀觀眾休息<br />\n係同基友休息吹水 同埋 避走地洞時都要嚇一嚇你<br />\n<br />\n真係睇到熱淚盈眶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e16aa1c1d8c72bf5ed2d8a4dd08df830e770e4","tid":58969,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瞓醒未"},{"pid":"b425fbf319922970a58ff2cbeae61d203241c4fe","tid":58969,"uid":18722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"認真定假膠？<br />\n鋼鋸嶺人物刻劃單一，雷霆救兵成隊士命都刻劃得好突岀。<br />\n雷霆唔止贏一班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f615b2b6b0cc8b5f57fe983a4821d76577bc23","tid":58969,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"唔覺，雷霆救兵最後阿伯向墳墓敬禮果到次次睇到喊"},{"pid":"087ac098ded9d67929fe35fd9b7e084b21ac041a","tid":58969,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"雷霆救兵一開波就埋牙搶灘真係經典<br />\n細個第一次睇見到有個兵比人炸斷手執返起係度四圍遊好深刻"},{"pid":"c164258597543a70b1e737edfa2af494b38592c8","tid":58969,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得雷霆救兵到中段好悶 <br />\n拖太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780f80b397035838ba341fcf9f7936bbcb9aefcc","